{"tid":2141804,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解00後後獨立高達系列，除咗00都柒下柒下","createTime":"2020-08-06T03:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T20:20:09.000Z","uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"eaad2c2be52f1d1ad02aeb22eb418e26114afba2","tid":2141804,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"雖然00抄unicorn互相理解，但起碼都講到國際政治，有獨家嘢，太陽爐設計又夠夢幻，機設四平八穩靠唔錯，嘟做有UC級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其他啲乜種子、鐵血嘅劇情都係虎頭蛇尾，尤其種子啲劇情極MK加特輯feel，只會用高達皮而無高達精神，主角開無雙得嚟性格唔討好（鐵血相反，角色討好而劇情柒）<br />\n<br />\nUC由元祖、08小隊到馬反一直都保持到高質劇情、人性探討，高達味濃厚，到0096雖然有少少MK但收尾夠震撼夠epic，長篇得嚟有新意，撐起高達個banner<br />\n<br />\n明明90年代仲有W同機武傳呢啲有創意得嚟夠高質嘅高達，到00後就真係得翻00<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5c8e07adc6484d322995bac02320e12a29deb6","tid":2141804,"uid":191467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"00 種子好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db38e25001d5f55a3010800ec41e7fd1d2ffcc09","tid":2141804,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4b5c8e07adc6484d322995bac02320e12a29deb6","tid":2141804,"uid":191467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"00 種子好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"種子咪MK肥皂劇，邊有高達精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96292d4e4954e926be723e0c2f5c77f91473e302","tid":2141804,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"db38e25001d5f55a3010800ec41e7fd1d2ffcc09","tid":2141804,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4b5c8e07adc6484d322995bac02320e12a29deb6","tid":2141804,"uid":191467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"00 種子好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class